<% 
  title 'Rates &amp; Policies'
  desc =<<-DESC.strip
    Suzanne Can has a straight-forward pricing structure and common-sense
    policies.  Rates from $20 to $40 per hour depending upon what you need.   
  DESC
  description desc
  kws =<<-KWS.strip
    service rates,basic services,plus services,premium services,reservations,
    reminder services,online purchases,research,errands,mileage,travel
  KWS
  keywords kws
%>
<div id="main">
  <h1>Rates</h1>
  <p>
    Its real simple.  I charge by the hour with a one hour minimum and I have
    three service level tiers.
  </p>
  <table id="service-rates" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
      <td class="service-level">Basic</td>
      <td class="service-rate">$20/hr</td>
      <td class="service-desc">
        <a href="/services#basic-services">
          These services consist of any tasks performed at my office on your 
          behalf (e.g. reservations, reminder services, online purchases, research, 
          etc.) 
        </a>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="service-level">Plus</td>
      <td class="service-rate">$25/hr</td>
      <td class="service-desc">
        <a href="/services#plus-services">
          These services include any tasks that require pickup or delivery, 
          waiting services (up to 4 hours), and generally any errands performed
          outside my office.
        </a>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="service-level">Premium</td>
      <td class="service-rate">$40/hr</td>
      <td class="service-desc">
        <a href="/services#premium-services">
          These services include any organizing, decorating, entertaining, or 
          event planning projects which involve additional time, resources, and
          coordination. 
        </a>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <h2>Policies</h2>
  <ul id="policy-list">
    <li>
      <p>
        Standard business hours are Monday through Friday, 8:30am to 5:30pm.
        Service requests outside of normal business hours will be subject to
        an additional charge of $10 per hour (if accepted).
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        A 24-hour notice is requested on all services.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        A 24 hour notice for any cancellation is requested.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        There is a one-hour minimum on all requests for service.  Service calls
        that exceed a one-hour period will be calculated at 15-minute intervals.
        Thus, you will not lose a full hour for a 90-minute service call.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        Materials, expenses, and taxes are all additional charges on top of the
        hourly rates.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        Mileage is included in the hourly rate for travel within a 20-mile
        perimeter.  Travel beyond that distance will be charged an additional
        rate of 45Â¢ per mile.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        All information regarding clients of Suzanne Can is held in the 
        strictest confidence and is not shared with anyone.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        All services will be performed by Suzanne Can as efficiently and 
        safely as possible.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        Suzanne Can reserves the right of refusal to participate in activities
        deemed dangerous, illegal, or unethical.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>

